Module com.cyslide
Package com.cyslide.Model

Class Level

java.lang.Object
com.cyslide.Model.Level
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
public class Level extends Object implements Cloneable
The Level class represents a game level in CySlide. It contains information about the level number, move counter, randomization status, completion status, record, and the game table. The class provides methods for retrieving and modifying these properties, as well as recovering level data from files, moving tiles, and checking level completion.
